reviews: I bought 2 of these to work, outside in the summer and cover my tattoos. They re tough, yet light and breathable. great quality and price. I would buy again.
Exactly as described. Great product for the price!

Bought this as a gift for my uncle who owns a 1969 Mach 1 fastback. I read through the book before I gave it to him. Regardless if you own the car or are just a fan of the car this book is absolutely incredible. The amount of knowledge inside is crazy. I didn’t think there would be near that amount of information in this book. From the history to how to maintain and fix the car. Great photos and great information.

16$ for a toque that is super well made and durable. I have a bunch of different colours. Another thing I love is they are MADE in Canada. Where can you find something of this quality for that price that is made at home? Great job Carhartt!
25$ for 5 BLURAYS. Can’t go wrong with that! Quick delivery, great product.

Great product. Easy to use and make the apartment smell great. I love using this thing while I sleep. Put some lavender in there and you’ll sleep like a baby. I also love using it when I’m sick. I usually mix lavender and either peppermint or eucalyptus. Great product for the price, I’ve seen these identical models in store for more than double the price.

I was shocked when I opened this keyboard. The build quality is outstanding. It’s a bit heavy but that’s ok because it’s built really well. The key strokes and keys are really nice and smooth as well. Took me 2 seconds to connect to my iPad. I would definitely highly recommend this product.
